reviewText: not as good as the previous series.
As with the previous 4 series of Stella this series was fantastic! I love the characters and the actors who portray them I love Ruth Jones. I hope there will be a series 6.
Another great season of Stella.  One of my favorite shows.  I laughed; I cried.
Have to watch it from season 1 thur 5 if there is a six season I would like to order it.  Stella is warm and funny.  She makes you laugh and cry just like any family.
